Rescuers work at the landslide site after a heavy rain near the tourist spot Shimla in Himachal Pradesh, India, on Aug. 18, 2019. Over 40 people have died in rain-related incidents in India's northern states of Himachal Pradesh, Uttarakhand and Punjab in the last 24 hours, media reports said on Monday. (Xinhua/Stringer)  

